<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ shop.name }} — Em Breve</title>
  {{ content_for_header }}
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@200;300&family=Jost:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
    body{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#fff;font-family:Jost,sans-serif;text-align:center;padding:40px 20px}
    .pw-logo{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:300;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:6px;line-height:1.4;margin-bottom:48px}
    h1{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:300;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:12px}
    p{font-size:12px;color:#767676;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:40px}
    .pw-form{display:flex;gap:0;max-width:400px;width:100%}
    .pw-form input{flex:1;border:1px solid #E5E5E5;border-right:none;padding:13px 16px;font-family:Jost,sans-serif;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:1px;outline:none}
    .pw-form button{background:#111;color:#fff;border:none;padding:13px 24px;font-family:Jost,sans-serif;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;cursor:pointer}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="pw-logo">NATALIA<br>SILVEIRA</div>
  <h1>EM BREVE</h1>
  <p>Algo especial está chegando.<br>Cadastre-se para ser a primeira a saber.</p>

  {%- form 'storefront_password' -%}
    <div class="pw-form">
      <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Senha" autocomplete="current-password">
      <button type="submit">ENTRAR</button>
    </div>
    {{ form.errors | default_errors }}
  {%- endform -%}
</body>
</html>
